    "date": "2024-06-21T13:32:33Z",
    "text": "Community Facilities Program for Rural Clean School Bus Infrastructure Act\n\nThis bill expands the essential community facilities direct loan and grant program of the Department of Agriculture to allow loans or grants to be used for deploying clean school buses and related infrastructure. Specifically, loans or grants may be used for (1) acquisition and labor costs for charging or other infrastructure needed to charge or maintain clean school buses, or (2) planning and technical activities to support the adoption and deployment of clean school buses."
